member.summary:
Gripper Y/Z device interface.

A gripper Y/Z device is a complex device used to transfer Items. It includes 
all needed stuff for transferring objects with rotation option.
This interface is defined for usage in the \nlink{Sias.GripArm,SHandlingMethods}
arm methods class.
Important classes implementing IGripYZDevice: 
 - \nlink{Sias.GripArm,SGripYZDevice}
 - \nlink{Sias.CombiArm,SCombiYZDevice}
 .
